Direct Known Subclasses:
TagConstants
public class TagConstants
extends OperatorTags

Tags is a class defining a partially-opaque type for tags used in the AST. "Partially opaque" means that the representation of this type is known -- it's an int -- but code should not depend on the detailed mapping of operator tags to integers.
